Ask Dang: why is the dupe detector broken?
text:
I've seen the same story about levels.fyi submitted 10 times over the last ~10 days. I can see why, because it's a cool story and very relevant toHN's readership, but it's baffling to me to see the same story popping up again and again. I run into the dupe detector regularly as a submitter, I wonder why it stops working in some cases.
